{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b52ccd65fc","title":"关于修筑铁路等问题致陈云、薄一波电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fdc4d8ace5","index":0,"year":1950,"month":1,"day":10,"articleId":"b52ccd65fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"a2f6c6af57","name":"陈云","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"1bdc3136f6","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52ccd65fc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，当时任政务院副总理兼财政经济委员会主任。薄一波，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任。"},{"id":"f6aed587e1","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52ccd65fc","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指陈云、薄一波1950年1月7日关于财政经济的几项情况给毛泽东并中央的报告。"}],"contents":[{"id":"affad43d2a","type":"title","text":"关于修筑铁路等问题致陈云、薄一波电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52ccd65fc"},{"id":"1bdc3136f6","type":"paragraph","text":"陈云、一波：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52ccd65fc"},{"id":"f6aed587e1","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）一月七日电悉，此项报告甚好，盼能继续。（二）各项计划均好，用军队修筑天兰天成成渝叙昆滇黔黔桂湘桂诸线甚为必要，望即着手布置进行。（三）去年十月一日以后在中财委领导下开了多次专业会议，除铁路，钢铁，农业三项已见一月七日来电外，其他各项会议结果的要点我手边没有材料，请于数日内分项写一报告给我，未知你们能腾得时间否。如你们无时间，可否要你们的秘书写，经你们看过发来。不要太繁，每项几百字即够。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52ccd65fc"},{"id":"48a9d3bda1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52ccd65fc"},{"id":"896a84713d","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52ccd65fc"}],"page":{"id":"2b4dc4b698","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52ccd65fc","start":155,"end":155}}}},"__N_SSG":true}